Package: caladown
Type: Package
Title: A Hugo Theme for R users
Version: 0.2.1
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Danielle",
           family = "Navarro",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "d.navarro@unsw.edu.au",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-7648-6578"))
Description: Provides a simple theme for building websites with blogdown or 
    hugodown. The caladown package contains wrapper functions to install the 
    calade theme for Hugo, ensures that the user has the necessary R packages
    required to build the site.
